OL,3,CRedcar residents stand in solidarity
OL,4,Cwith Port Talbot steelworkers
OL,6,FResidents of Redcar are standing in
OL,7,Fsolidarity with steelworkers in Wales
OL,8,Fwho have lost their jobs.
OL,10,FTata Steel announced in January its
OL,11,Frestructuring plans involve cutting
OL,12,F2,800 UK jobs and will also include
OL,13,Fthe installation of an electric
OL,14,Ffurnace using recycled steel.
OL,16,FThe announcement brought back bad
OL,17,Fmemories for former Teesside
OL,18,Fsteelworker Charlie Elcoate.
